1.4.0 (2014-11-28)
  - fixed alert removal order
  - made alert remove timeout configurable
  - added handling of "preinstall" and "postinstall" hooks for recipes, possible values are "type" [alert|overlay], "message" (any text) and "link" (url to README etc.)
    which are displayed before/after download of modules. The default "type" for preinstall is "alert", for postinstall "overlay".
    
1.3.0 (2014-11-27)
  - automatically remove alert messages after some seconds
  - code cleanup
  
1.2.2 (2014-11-25)
  - bugfix for OXID >= 4.9.0
  
1.2.1 (2014-11-22)
  - add module version in tpl

1.2.0 (2014-11-21)
  - add recipe filter
  
1.1.0 (2014-11-16)
  - add multiple cookbooks
  - update CLI functions
  
1.0.0 (2014-11-12)
